==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Tigris'''
#A 1150-meter-long river in Southwest [[Asia]]. It flows east-southeast and forms the eastern edge of classical [[Mesopotamia]]. It unites with the [[Euphrates]] River before flowing into the [[Persian Gulf]].

